Package com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NNExecutionContext
    This base class is passed into any NNLayer evaluation code to communicate context information.
    Tensor.TupleOperator
    The interface Tuple operator.
    TensorList
    This abstract data container is used to pass data between NNLayer components.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Coordinate
    A data structure to represent an index/coordinate/tuple for referencing elements in a Tensor.
    Delta<K>
    An arithmetic delta being staged to effect an in-memory change to a double[] array.
    DeltaSet<K>
    This is a collection of Deltas being staged for particular layers.
    DoubleArrayStatsFacade
    The type Double array stats facade.
    DoubleBuffer<K>
    A generic alternate memory buffer being staged in relation to an existing double[] array.
    DoubleBufferSet<K,T extends DoubleBuffer<K>>
    A collection of DoubleBuffer objects being staged for particular layers.
    NNConstant
    A special type of NNResult which ignores backpropigation; it has a constant value.
    NNLayer
    The basic type of Neural Network Layer supporting the backpropigation model of learning.
    NNResult
    This type holds the result from a NNLayer evaluation.
    PointSample
    Represents an evaluation record used during an optimization search.
    RecycleBin<T>
    This is a recycling mechanism to reuse short-term-lifecycle T objects of regular length.
    StackCounter
    The type Stack counter.
    StackCounter.StackFrame
    The type Stack frame.
    State<K>
    Alternate version being staged to effect an in-memory change to a double[] array.
    StateSet<K>
    A collection of State objects being staged for particular layers.
    Tensor
    A multi-dimensional array of data.
    TensorArray
    An on-heap implementation of the TensorList data container.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    RecycleBin.PersistanceMode
    The enum Persistance mode.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ComponentException
    An exception occured within a NNLayer component.
    GpuError
    A low-level exception occured while executing GPU instructions
    IterativeStopException
    Used to communicate that an iterative learning process should be terminated gracefully.
    OutOfMemoryError
    A custom type for OOM errors so we can track an inner exception.
